| Detection 4: Process Discovery (T1057)
| Trigger: tasklist or Get-Process used to enumerate running processes
| Severity: Medium
| ATT&CK: T1057 - Process Discovery

index=main source="WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational"
| rex field=_raw "CommandLine'>(?<CommandLine>[^<]+)"
| rex field=_raw "Image'>(?<Image>[^<]+)"
| search CommandLine="*tasklist*" OR CommandLine="*Get-Process*"
| table _time, Image, CommandLine
| sort _time
